
steps :  
=> ng new flowers-shop --inline-style --inline-template

=> ng g s flowers --flat

=> OPEN CODE editor

=> fill up the service list

=> create the flowers list component : ng g c flowersList --flat --standalone

=> create the flowers card component : ng g c flowerCard --flat --standalone

==> display the list using the app.module and just call the flowers list component in the app component

=> create route for the list component 

=> display it  with routing 

=>  create the flowers view component : ng g c viewFlower --flat --standalone

=> add the router details in the routes list 

=> NOW => modify the app.component to be standalone with imports to the routerMOdule 

=> then modify the main.ts to boostrap the application with providers

